  "texts": [
    "Participants were given two prompts shown independently: \"Imagine humans no longer needed sleep, \" and \"Imagine humans walked with their hands.\"",
    "The two CT prompts have been extensively used in research on divergent thinking [41] [42] [43].",
    "Similar to the AUT, fluency and timing parameters were excluded from the GPT instructions on the CT:",
    "In this task, a statement will appear on the screen.",
    "The statement might be something like \"imagine gravity ceases to exist\"."
